Yes—good news: the right pane renders because it’s your local clone. The left pane (the original site) is almost certainly being blocked by the site’s security headers (X-Frame-Options and/or CSP frame-ancestors), so the iframe can’t load it inside your page. That’s why it “doesn’t execute”.
